{"tid":318628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［沒有小鳥的天空］5歲男童慘遭保母夫滾水淋下體 緊急割J求生","createTime":"2017-07-12T08:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T08:32:13.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cff161091b588f0648427eadf109aca16e6eb85b","tid":318628,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"保母夫婦用熱水潑5歲男童　下體燙傷「去勢」保命<br />\n 泰國一名5歲男童，日前遭保母和她的丈夫虐待，竟然被惡意潑熱水，導致下體和腹部嚴重燙傷。醫院診治後為了要保住男童的性命，最後只好將他「去勢」，讓人看了十分心疼與不捨。<br />\n <br />\n根據《都會報》(Metro)報導，這起保母夫妻虐待5歲男童的案件，發生在今年1月。據悉男童的母親長期在外地工作，因此將孩子托育給保母照顧。當時保母的丈夫不知什麼原因，宣稱要懲罰男童，竟然拿滾燙的熱水朝他潑去，導致腹部以下嚴重燙傷。<br />\n <br />\n男童事後被送醫治療，醫師診斷情況嚴重，必須要「去勢」才能保住一命。<br />\n <br />\n男童的母親表示，她每天都有打電話到保母家，關心兒子的狀況；但直到某日對方突然不和她通電話，讓她直覺有異狀，事後才得知兒子出事了。<br />\n <br />\n更令男童母親不滿的是，她曾報警處理，但當地警方拖了半年，至今都沒任何進一步的動作，直到最近請了一名王牌律師，案情才重啟調查。另外還傳出保母的丈夫原是一名空軍軍官，但虐童事件發生後已經遭到解雇。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/745512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F745512&d=fWioDdguaSyGQqllMOCZiAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=875d48c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/745512</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/12/161333_93e6f730418b666ebcd44925e1590e7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F12%2F161333_93e6f730418b666ebcd44925e1590e7f.jpg&h=ecb493f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好慘，睇到都痛、但男童心靈更痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db4dbea4e075a42424c9ce536bc9c0bd65ad10b","tid":318628,"uid":10165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"慎入呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1596534916b2cbea98d0db9c69338bbb6358f535","tid":318628,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"好撚想淋番保母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c313ff8e81cfc15beb21ddbf0e4e3e509b39f2","tid":318628,"uid":127789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚想淋番保母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n佢好撚衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f63d28885df22ac5faf8a8a895a8e9baefa60f","tid":318628,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}